{"TopicId":150542,"ForumId":21,"TopicTitle":"[stock] heavy load trailer hitch","CreatedByName":"katateochi","CreatedById":35181,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-21T21:52:56Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"katateochi","CreatedById":35181,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-21T21:52:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA simple but very strong stock trailer hitch\u00A0that\u0027s able to tow heavy loads.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt uses 4 medium landing leg to create a socket with an I-beam under it (that the trailer hitch rests on). \u00A0The hitch itself is a small landing gear. \u00A0That\u0027s it, not much else to it.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022aDznvip.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022623\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/aDznvip.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022dGlscSC.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022623\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/dGlscSC.jpg\u0022 style=\u0022width:500px;height:auto;\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022zsqCmVR.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022623\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/zsqCmVR.jpg\u0022 style=\u0022width:500px;height:auto;\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWith the trailer shown the truck is able to drive at reasonable speeds and can (with a short run-up) make it up slopes.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s also quite stable over scene reloads and when switching between craft, trailer sometimes jumps a bit, but it doesn\u0027t break.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ECraft file -\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://kerbalx.com/katateochi/GroundSupport-FuelRig\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://kerbalx.com/katateochi/GroundSupport-FuelRig\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nIt can be used to pull much heavier loads, just oh so very much slower, and you can forget about driving up slopes!\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022sQNbEPH.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022622\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/sQNbEPH.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Majorjim!","CreatedById":61954,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-22T08:25:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGreat work kat! Perfect solution for big heavy loads.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-10-22T08:25:57Z\u0022 title=\u002210/22/2016 08:25  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 22, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Majorjim!\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bloojay","CreatedById":162865,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-28T09:12:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNice bit of equipment\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}